   :alt: Documentation Status
.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/ics2todoist.svg?style=flat
   :alt: Python Versions
   :target: https://pypi.org/project/ics2todoist/
.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/ics2todoist.svg?style=flat
